snippet.title: JanKen Battle Arena Announcement Trailer (Android)
snippet.description:
The battle for supremacy of Rock, Paper and Scissors master (JanKen masters) have begun. Play against fellow players or friends to earn coins to collect more characters, items and weapons. 

Get ready to experience a Rock, Paper and Scissors game like you have never played it before. 

Google Play: https://goo.gl/eg5BvQ

For more information please go to:

Facebook Page: https://www.facebook.com/JanKenBattleArena/
Official Page: http://playplayfun.com/janken-battle-arena-game-official-page/
